{"data":[{"id":563667922,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563667922","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546263582,"updated_time":1546263582,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":8,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e先一本正经地回答问题\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e问：如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e答：不能，不符合国家规定的保送条件，保送生有且只有以下五类：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1.省级优秀学生\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e2.高中学科竞赛(数，物，化，生，信)国家集训队队员\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e3.高水平运动员\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e4.具有推荐保送生资格的外国语中学推荐保送的高中生\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e5.公安英烈子女\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但可以报清华北大的自主招生了，因为符合自主招生中的下列条件：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e在科技发明、研究实践、文学创作等方面具有突出表现的学生\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e还极有可能获得国家最高科学技术奖。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e——————分割线——————\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e再说明一下，高中生证明哥德巴赫猜想是不可能的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e哥德巴赫猜想虽然小学生都能看懂，但要解决它需要解析数论中极为高深的知识，高中知识的广度和深度远不及此。而且，高中时期连初等数论都没有，就更不用说解析数论了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我想我作为一名上过高中的学生，指出题主证明中的错误还是可以的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e还有就是不得不说这是个涨粉的好方法，在这个娱乐至上的时代里，有流量有人气还有什么干不成的？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这个提问已经给题主带来了足够多的资源，就看如何去运用了。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"先一本正经地回答问题问：如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？答：不能，不符合国家规定的保送条件，保送生有且只有以下五类：1.省级优秀学生2.高中学科竞赛(数，物，化，生，信)国家集训队队员3.高水平运动员4.具有推荐保送生资格的…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=97\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerp